cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper deals with unsupervised analysis of image-derived features using deep learning models, feature selection, and clustering. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the use of MRIs and medical imaging techniques suggests a possible fit with multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
